jobs.jobRequirements:
Must have experience caring for young children, preferably toddlers or preschool-aged.

Be patient, caring, and energetic, able to handle two active 4-year-olds at the same time.

Responsible for daily care routines, including bathing, feeding, dressing, and supervising playtime.

Able to create a safe and nurturing environment for both children.

Engage children in educational and creative activities (reading, drawing, singing, storytelling, learning games, etc.).

jobs.jobRequirements: Looking for a helper to take care of an elderly couple. Main duties include assisting them with daily routines, preparing meals, keeping their area clean, and ensuring their comfort and safety. Must be kind, patient, and responsible. No need to take care of the baby, as we already have another helper for that. Basic cooking and general housework are required. Experience in elderly care is preferred.
